     <lb/>
            </p>
   
            <p>
     On item $1,300,000, for opening communica<lb break="no"/>tion with, establishing a government in, and 
     <lb/>
     providing for the Settlement in the North-West 
     <lb/>
     (re-vote), 
     <lb/>
            </p>
   
            <p>
     <persName ref="pers:MASS3">Mr. Masson</persName> (Soulanges) moved that the 
     <lb/>
     words be added "providing that no portion of 
     <lb/>
